                    "line_text": "C’était Jame ! et la fiancée",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Vint toucher, à sa main glacée,",
